*ghc-bin-5.04.2 (21 Mar 2003)

  21 Mar 2003; George Shapovalov <george@gentoo.org> ghc-bin-5.04.2.ebuild :
  created virtual/ghc, added PROVIDE=virtual/ghc to the ebuild to make dev-lang/ghc bootstrap correctly
